OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud and
OL,6,Fpatchy rain may move into the far west
OL,7,Fat times overnight. Otherwise dry with
OL,8,Fclear spells, but some mist and fog
OL,9,Fpatches may develop, especially in the
OL,10,Feast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FThe far west continuing to
OL,13,Fsee some cloud and patchy rain at
OL,14,Ftimes. Elsewhere, any mist and fog
OL,15,Fclearing allowing some bright or sunny
OL,16,Fspells to develop. Feeling very mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
