OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,6,Fmoving across the region on Thursday
OL,7,Fbefore turning brighter with some
OL,8,Fshowers on Friday. Further rain likely
OL,9,Flater on Saturday. Temperatures
OL,10,Freturning to nearer average.
